Mappings
--------
Four C++ abstract base classes are provided for the purpose of subclassing.
The four types cover autonomous/non-autonomous exogenous/endogenous systems.

Documentation
-------------
Doxygen is used to document each class.  You can build the documentation if you
have doxygen installed, simply type

   $ make doc

Example
-------
test_mappings.cc is an example of use for a pendulum, a pendulum with joint
torque, and a Henon map.  You can build the example with

   $ make
